Use these source code files to supplement the textbook "Flexible
Reliable Software, by Christensen" in classroom activities. These are
simple, one file C++ source code to start-up discussion on various
topics.

1) Introducing the Strategy design pattern (Chapter 7). Variabllity.

   greeter.cc
   ----------
   Extend the greeter class so that different greetings can be
   produced (for example in French, German, Romanian, Hungarian,
   etc...). 
